  "detailed_description": "<i><strong>Welcome to Reshape,</strong></i><br>the ultimate physics-based sandbox design game that offers unparalleled freedom and creativity! Dive into a world where you can pick up, throw, freeze, rotate, and manipulate objects in countless ways, limited only by your imagination.<br><br><i><strong>Key Features:</strong></i><br><br><strong><i><u>Limitless Creativity:</u></i></strong><br>With a vast array of items including tables, chairs, beds, flowers, cars, and weapons, Reshape gives you the tools to create anything you can imagine.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782520/extras/75ad4096bf356941ff3c09c658af0464.poster.avif?t=1726933066\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782520/extras/75ad4096bf356941ff3c09c658af0464.webm?t=1726933066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782520/extras/75ad4096bf356941ff3c09c658af0464.mp4?t=1726933066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><i><u>Dynamic Physics:</u></i></strong><br>Experience a realistic and dynamic physics engine that allows for endless interactions and creative possibilities.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782520/extras/18bb8db2e4e3bb46f452b9af4b899978.poster.avif?t=1726933066\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782520/extras/18bb8db2e4e3bb46f452b9af4b899978.webm?t=1726933066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782520/extras/18bb8db2e4e3bb46f452b9af4b899978.mp4?t=1726933066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><i><u>Interactive Environment:</u></i></strong><br>Explore a fully interactive environment where every object can be manipulated and every action has a reaction.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782520/extras/3db82bd04b1bc8f5d8c389f1c05529e8.poster.avif?t=1726933066\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782520/extras/3db82bd04b1bc8f5d8c389f1c05529e8.webm?t=1726933066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782520/extras/3db82bd04b1bc8f5d8c389f1c05529e8.mp4?t=1726933066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><i><strong>Sandbox Freedom:</strong></i></u><br>There are no rules or objectives in Reshape – just pure, unadulterated creativity. Build, destroy, or simply experiment to your heart's content.<br><br>Reshape offers a universe of possibilities where your creativity knows no bounds. Whether you're a seasoned designer or just looking to unleash your creative side, Reshape is the ultimate playground for your imagination. Start creating today and reshape the world around you!",
  "about_the_game": "<i><strong>Welcome to Reshape,</strong></i><br>the ultimate physics-based sandbox design game that offers unparalleled freedom and creativity! Dive into a world where you can pick up, throw, freeze, rotate, and manipulate objects in countless ways, limited only by your imagination.<br><br><i><strong>Key Features:</strong></i><br><br><strong><i><u>Limitless Creativity:</u></i></strong><br>With a vast array of items including tables, chairs, beds, flowers, cars, and weapons, Reshape gives you the tools to create anything you can imagine.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782520/extras/75ad4096bf356941ff3c09c658af0464.poster.avif?t=1726933066\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782520/extras/75ad4096bf356941ff3c09c658af0464.webm?t=1726933066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782520/extras/75ad4096bf356941ff3c09c658af0464.mp4?t=1726933066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><i><u>Dynamic Physics:</u></i></strong><br>Experience a realistic and dynamic physics engine that allows for endless interactions and creative possibilities.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782520/extras/18bb8db2e4e3bb46f452b9af4b899978.poster.avif?t=1726933066\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782520/extras/18bb8db2e4e3bb46f452b9af4b899978.webm?t=1726933066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782520/extras/18bb8db2e4e3bb46f452b9af4b899978.mp4?t=1726933066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><i><u>Interactive Environment:</u></i></strong><br>Explore a fully interactive environment where every object can be manipulated and every action has a reaction.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782520/extras/3db82bd04b1bc8f5d8c389f1c05529e8.poster.avif?t=1726933066\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782520/extras/3db82bd04b1bc8f5d8c389f1c05529e8.webm?t=1726933066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782520/extras/3db82bd04b1bc8f5d8c389f1c05529e8.mp4?t=1726933066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><i><strong>Sandbox Freedom:</strong></i></u><br>There are no rules or objectives in Reshape – just pure, unadulterated creativity. Build, destroy, or simply experiment to your heart's content.<br><br>Reshape offers a universe of possibilities where your creativity knows no bounds. Whether you're a seasoned designer or just looking to unleash your creative side, Reshape is the ultimate playground for your imagination. Start creating today and reshape the world around you!",
